data.description: THIS BEAUTIFUL MOVE-IN READY HOME IS WELL-MAINTAINED AND OFFERS 5 BEDROOMS & 2.5 BATHS. THE 2-STORY ENTRY FOYER LEADS TO THE DINING ROOM & LOVELY GREAT ROOM WITH VAULTED CEILING & FIREPLACE W/GAS LOGS. THE SPACIOUS MASTER IS ON THE MAIN AND FEATURES A LOVELY TREY CEILING & WONDERFUL MASTER BATH WITH DOUBLE VANITIES, A WHIRLPOOL TUB, SEPARATE SHOWER, PRIVATE WATER CLOSET AND A SPACIOUS WALK-IN CLOSET! THE KITCHEN HAS BEAUTIFUL TILE FLOORS, SOLID SURFACE COUNTER TOPS, AMPLE CABINETS AND A COZY BREAKFAST AREA. THERE IS A CONVENIENT LAUNDRY ROOM LOCATED OFF THE KITCHEN. THE UPSTAIRS FEATURES BEAUTIFUL HARDWOOD FLOORING IN THE HALL LEADING TO 4 BEDROOMS & A FULL BATH. THE .77 ACRE LOT HAS A SPACIOUS FRONT YARD & HUGE PRIVATE BACK YARD SURROUNDED BY A WOODEN PRIVACY FENCE. THERE IS A BEAUTIFUL OVERSIZED DECK WITH MULTIPLE SITTING AREAS AND CONVENIENT AWNING TO PROTECT FROM RAIN AND DIRECT SUNLIGHT. THERE ARE 2 COMMUNITY SWIMMING POOLS AND 2 TENNIS COURTS - ONE TENNIS COURT IS DESIGNATED FOR PICKLE BALL. LOCATED JUST MINUTES AWAY FROM SHOPPING AND AMAZING SCHOOLS, THIS GREAT FAMILY HOME WILL NOT LAST LONG!
